WEBVTT

00:00:00.600 --> 00:00:03.350
Well, good morning family. It's

00:00:04.400 --> 00:00:06.190
late night, almost early

00:00:06.200 --> 00:00:08.310
morning, but I thought I'd pray with you

00:00:08.310 --> 00:00:08.320
all

00:00:08.320 --> 00:00:10.470
for a little bit. We went

00:00:10.480 --> 00:00:14.030
to the Branson

00:00:14.040 --> 00:00:16.870
prayer conference and what a time

00:00:16.880 --> 00:00:18.150
we had.

00:00:18.160 --> 00:00:21.550
It was wonderful. How's my audio? Tell

00:00:21.560 --> 00:00:23.630
us in the comment section down below

00:00:23.640 --> 00:00:25.870
how the audio is. We're trying a new mic

00:00:25.880 --> 00:00:27.750
because it echoes a lot, so

00:00:27.760 --> 00:00:29.270
we're trying to make it so you can

00:00:29.280 --> 00:00:30.750
hear us better.

00:00:30.760 --> 00:00:32.109
Let us know; if

00:00:32.109 --> 00:00:32.119
it's

00:00:32.119 --> 00:00:33.750
bad, we can switch back. I can push one

00:00:33.760 --> 00:00:35.590
button and it'll go back to the old

00:00:35.600 --> 00:00:37.550
one. If you don't like it, let us

00:00:37.560 --> 00:00:39.550
know.

00:00:39.560 --> 00:00:41.830
But we went to the prayer conference in

00:00:41.840 --> 00:00:45.270
Branson and it was wonderful. I

00:00:45.280 --> 00:00:47.550
really enjoyed that with Sister Billie

00:00:47.560 --> 00:00:51.630
and the family and Lynn and

00:00:51.640 --> 00:00:54.270
so many other people. They came from all

00:00:54.280 --> 00:00:55.950
over the place and it was awesome to

00:00:55.960 --> 00:00:59.030
see everybody.

00:00:59.030 --> 00:00:59.040
At

00:00:59.040 --> 00:01:02.310
the tent meeting we prayed;

00:01:02.320 --> 00:01:04.390
it wasn't live,

00:01:04.400 --> 00:01:07.030
televised, or

00:01:07.040 --> 00:01:08.230
livestreamed.

00:01:08.240 --> 00:01:10.950
There

00:01:10.950 --> 00:01:10.960
were

00:01:10.960 --> 00:01:13.390
demonstrations and manifestations.

00:01:13.400 --> 00:01:16.950
Pastor Tracy Harris from Texarkana came

00:01:16.960 --> 00:01:19.230
and laid hands on everyone in

00:01:19.240 --> 00:01:21.150
the whole

00:01:21.160 --> 00:01:24.110
tent revival and the power of God

00:01:24.120 --> 00:01:26.550
was knocking people down. It was

00:01:26.560 --> 00:01:30.030
amazing to see people get so blessed.

00:01:30.040 --> 00:01:33.190
Then they had the fish fry, but I

00:01:33.200 --> 00:01:34.790
got to speak

00:01:34.800 --> 00:01:38.710
at that tent meeting and that was the

00:01:38.720 --> 00:01:41.470
first time I've ever

00:01:41.480 --> 00:01:44.150
spoken to that many people for

00:01:44.160 --> 00:01:47.270
that long. Usually I talk

00:01:47.280 --> 00:01:49.710
a little bit and I've done that

00:01:49.720 --> 00:01:51.390
several times, but this is the first

00:01:51.400 --> 00:01:53.390
time anyone has really

00:01:53.400 --> 00:01:54.590
handed me the mic and said 'go with

00:01:54.590 --> 00:01:54.600
it.'So

00:01:54.600 --> 00:01:57.030
it was a real blessing to

00:01:57.040 --> 00:02:00.390
be able to pray and do the things

00:02:00.400 --> 00:02:03.150
that the Lord allowed me to do

00:02:03.160 --> 00:02:05.470
during that service. I

00:02:05.480 --> 00:02:08.230
believe it went pretty well.

00:02:08.240 --> 00:02:10.230
How can you judge your own thing? I just

00:02:10.240 --> 00:02:11.710
go by

00:02:11.720 --> 00:02:13.550
what they all said, and

00:02:13.560 --> 00:02:15.510
they said it was good. So I'm thankful

00:02:15.520 --> 00:02:18.790
for it. But

00:02:18.800 --> 00:02:20.470
now we're home

00:02:20.480 --> 00:02:23.510
and

00:02:23.520 --> 00:02:25.830
I have an urgency in my spirit to pray

00:02:25.840 --> 00:02:28.630
for our economy,

00:02:28.640 --> 00:02:32.710
to keep praying

00:02:35.960 --> 00:02:38.350
against delays,

00:02:38.360 --> 00:02:39.870
coming against

00:02:39.880 --> 00:02:42.670
what I believe is the enemy trying to

00:02:42.680 --> 00:02:44.550
rear his head,

00:02:44.560 --> 00:02:46.790
trying to stop the blessing of what the

00:02:46.800 --> 00:02:49.270
Lord is wanting for this body.

00:02:50.480 --> 00:02:52.990
As I was driving around today,

00:02:53.000 --> 00:02:54.790
coming back into town and doing the

00:02:54.800 --> 00:02:57.390
things that the Lord wanted us to do, He

00:02:57.400 --> 00:03:00.870
said to me, 'Brandon,

00:03:00.880 --> 00:03:03.750
you're going to have to contend

00:03:03.760 --> 00:03:06.990
for what I've told you to do.

00:03:07.000 --> 00:03:09.070
Don't just lay down and say, "whatever

00:03:09.070 --> 00:03:09.080
will be,

00:03:09.080 --> 00:03:10.470
will be."'Like

00:03:10.470 --> 00:03:10.480
that song,

00:03:10.480 --> 00:03:13.510
'Whatever will be, will be,

00:03:13.520 --> 00:03:15.110
Que

00:03:15.120 --> 00:03:19.270
sera,

00:03:19.280 --> 00:03:20.310
sera.'It's

00:03:20.320 --> 00:03:22.470
not like that. We have got to

00:03:22.480 --> 00:03:24.230
take our authority

00:03:24.240 --> 00:03:26.750
and we have got to start praying

00:03:26.760 --> 00:03:29.590
over what God has told us to do and

00:03:29.600 --> 00:03:30.870
not just sit there and

00:03:30.870 --> 00:03:30.880
say,

00:03:30.880 --> 00:03:32.990
'Well, whatever will be, will

00:03:32.990 --> 00:03:33.000
be.'He

00:03:33.000 --> 00:03:34.710
said, 'Brandon, you're going to have

00:03:34.720 --> 00:03:35.950
to contend for it. You're going to have

00:03:35.960 --> 00:03:37.710
to fight for it,

00:03:37.720 --> 00:03:39.550
lay hold to

00:03:39.550 --> 00:03:39.560
it.'He

00:03:39.560 --> 00:03:42.230
said, 'Whenever I told the children

00:03:42.240 --> 00:03:46.550
of Israel to go and get the land,

00:03:46.560 --> 00:03:48.510
they had a choice.

00:03:48.520 --> 00:03:51.630
They could either say God is with us and

00:03:51.640 --> 00:03:53.470
who can be against us or have the

00:03:53.480 --> 00:03:56.070
attitude of a winner mentality, or you

00:03:56.080 --> 00:03:59.350
can shrink back and go, "well,

00:03:59.360 --> 00:04:01.550
we're the size of

00:04:01.550 --> 00:04:01.560
grasshoppers."'The

00:04:01.560 --> 00:04:03.910
first generation did that

00:04:03.920 --> 00:04:05.950
and they died in the wilderness.

00:04:05.960 --> 00:04:07.670
But God had to raise up a whole new

00:04:07.680 --> 00:04:09.510
generation of people

00:04:09.520 --> 00:04:12.230
to go and take the land for Him.

00:04:12.240 --> 00:04:13.790
And that's the kind of people that have

00:04:13.800 --> 00:04:17.069
the bulldog mentality that go after it like

00:04:17.079 --> 00:04:20.789
a dog on a bone and say, 'You know what?

00:04:20.799 --> 00:04:22.630
I'm fighting and contending for what's

00:04:22.640 --> 00:04:24.150
mine.'And

00:04:24.160 --> 00:04:26.230
the Lord told me,

00:04:26.230 --> 00:04:26.240
'For

00:04:26.240 --> 00:04:28.270
what I've

00:04:28.280 --> 00:04:30.190
called you to do, everything that I have,

00:04:30.200 --> 00:04:32.870
it's not

00:04:42.000 --> 00:04:43.630
a

00:04:43.640 --> 00:04:46.510
victim mentality that gets you there.

00:04:46.520 --> 00:04:48.910
You have a victor

00:04:48.920 --> 00:04:52.350
mentality, a winner mentality, but a

00:04:52.360 --> 00:04:54.870
winner mentality contends. They

00:04:54.880 --> 00:04:58.270
fight for it; they say, "This is

00:04:58.270 --> 00:04:58.280
mine."'Do

00:04:58.280 --> 00:05:00.190
you understand what I'm saying?

00:05:00.200 --> 00:05:03.350
It has to be that: how bad do you

00:05:03.360 --> 00:05:05.350
want it

00:05:05.360 --> 00:05:07.910
in these end times with all the stuff

00:05:07.920 --> 00:05:12.390
that's going on around us.

00:05:13.840 --> 00:05:15.390
There's so much every single

00:05:15.400 --> 00:05:17.710
day, ladies and gentlemen. I just

00:05:17.720 --> 00:05:19.510
go, 'My goodness, this has been

00:05:19.510 --> 00:05:19.520
incredible.'Even

00:05:19.520 --> 00:05:21.430
look at what

00:05:21.440 --> 00:05:23.590
we stopped, I believe, with the Atlanta

00:05:23.600 --> 00:05:25.710
shooting. The guy went in

00:05:27.120 --> 00:05:28.950
saying he wanted to do something at the

00:05:28.960 --> 00:05:32.630
airport, had 27

00:05:32.640 --> 00:05:36.310
shots and a firearm. He walked into

00:05:36.320 --> 00:05:38.830
the airport,

00:05:38.830 --> 00:05:38.840
but

00:05:38.840 --> 00:05:41.510
his family

00:05:41.520 --> 00:05:43.630
told on him and he was brought to

00:05:43.640 --> 00:05:45.750
justice by

00:05:45.760 --> 00:05:49.710
the police department there. Thank God

00:05:49.720 --> 00:05:51.710
that's an answer to prayer. That right

00:05:51.720 --> 00:05:53.710
there shows we're contending. We're

00:05:53.720 --> 00:05:55.910
fighting. We're saying, 'No, you're not

00:05:55.920 --> 00:05:58.790
going to do this to our

00:05:58.790 --> 00:05:58.800
airports.'Because

00:05:58.800 --> 00:06:00.630
bottom

00:06:00.640 --> 00:06:01.950
line, ladies and gentlemen, we wrestle

00:06:01.960 --> 00:06:03.910
not against flesh and blood;

00:06:03.920 --> 00:06:05.510
we're wrestling against principalities

00:06:05.520 --> 00:06:07.190
and powers and spiritual wickedness in

00:06:07.200 --> 00:06:10.630
high places. This

00:06:10.630 --> 00:06:10.640
was

00:06:10.640 --> 00:06:12.230
a principality working through a

00:06:12.240 --> 00:06:13.910
personality.

00:06:15.920 --> 00:06:18.030
But I believe as we are

00:06:18.040 --> 00:06:20.470
praying believers that come in agreement

00:06:20.480 --> 00:06:24.030
and intercede for our nation,

00:06:24.040 --> 00:06:26.510
we're stopping this stuff. Now, I

00:06:26.520 --> 00:06:28.870
believe there's a lot more to stop.

00:06:28.880 --> 00:06:33.110
But praying for our economy

00:06:33.120 --> 00:06:35.150
to turn around—there are so many people

00:06:35.160 --> 00:06:37.510
saying we're in a recession. There are so

00:06:37.520 --> 00:06:39.070
many people saying that it's worse

00:06:39.080 --> 00:06:41.510
than 2008,

00:06:41.520 --> 00:06:42.990
that it's going

00:06:43.000 --> 00:06:44.950
to get worse than that and go into the

00:06:44.960 --> 00:06:47.190
Great Depression. And

00:06:47.200 --> 00:06:49.670
I said, 'Not

00:06:49.680 --> 00:06:51.670
yet.'So

00:06:51.680 --> 00:06:53.150
that's why I wanted you to come on

00:06:53.160 --> 00:06:54.950
here and pray with me tonight

00:06:54.960 --> 00:06:57.190
to pray over our economy

00:06:57.190 --> 00:06:57.200
so

00:06:57.200 --> 00:07:00.350
that we have that window.

00:07:00.360 --> 00:07:02.510
Now, I know I've heard other people say

00:07:02.520 --> 00:07:03.790
they believe

00:07:03.800 --> 00:07:06.270
a great

00:07:06.280 --> 00:07:10.430
economic crisis worse than 2008 will come in

00:07:10.430 --> 00:07:10.440
the next year,

00:07:10.440 --> 00:07:12.830
but I believe in God

00:07:12.830 --> 00:07:12.840
for

00:07:12.840 --> 00:07:16.030
a supernatural wealth transfer for the

00:07:16.040 --> 00:07:18.030
body of Christ before all this starts to

00:07:18.040 --> 00:07:20.590
take place. I told you I saw

00:07:20.600 --> 00:07:24.190
President Trump treading the river.

00:07:24.200 --> 00:07:26.430
It was like Niagara Falls, and

00:07:26.440 --> 00:07:29.230
he was paddling as fast as he could

00:07:29.240 --> 00:07:31.590
because the boat was

00:07:31.600 --> 00:07:33.790
going to go over.

00:07:33.800 --> 00:07:36.630
But he was keeping

00:07:36.640 --> 00:07:39.430
the economy from going clear over by

00:07:39.440 --> 00:07:41.670
paddling in that canoe as fast as he

00:07:41.680 --> 00:07:43.630
could

00:07:43.640 --> 00:07:46.030
because he knew that it was just a

00:07:46.040 --> 00:07:48.270
matter of time and it was going over.

00:07:48.280 --> 00:07:50.870
It's going into the beast system.

00:07:50.880 --> 00:07:53.230
That's where all this is headed. We all

00:07:53.240 --> 00:07:55.390
know that a one-world government, a

00:07:55.390 --> 00:07:55.400
one-world

00:07:55.400 --> 00:07:58.710
financial system is coming

00:07:58.720 --> 00:08:00.350
because that's what the Bible says.

00:08:00.360 --> 00:08:02.470
And so if that's coming, we're

00:08:02.480 --> 00:08:04.230
not going to stop it.

00:08:04.240 --> 00:08:06.470
Can we delay it and give us more time? Yes.

00:08:06.480 --> 00:08:09.590
I believe with our prayers and as

00:08:09.600 --> 00:08:11.110
we intercede, we're the salt and the

00:08:11.120 --> 00:08:13.310
light of this world. I believe that God

00:08:13.320 --> 00:08:15.790
has given us the ability to change a

00:08:15.800 --> 00:08:17.870
lot of things through

00:08:17.870 --> 00:08:17.880
prayer—delaying

00:08:17.880 --> 00:08:19.590
things, doing things. But I'm

00:08:19.600 --> 00:08:21.910
going to tell you,

00:08:23.760 --> 00:08:26.070
we're running out of time. Jesus Christ

00:08:26.080 --> 00:08:27.790
is coming. Now, I

00:08:27.800 --> 00:08:30.470
heard another man this week

00:08:30.480 --> 00:08:33.110
say, 'We're so far away from all that.

00:08:33.120 --> 00:08:34.870
Don't worry,

00:08:34.880 --> 00:08:36.909
Jesus isn't coming right

00:08:36.919 --> 00:08:40.310
now.'I

00:08:40.320 --> 00:08:42.430
don't doubt that we have

00:08:42.440 --> 00:08:43.950
a lot to do,

00:08:43.960 --> 00:08:45.910
but I'm going to tell you this: the

00:08:45.920 --> 00:08:48.670
time clock is ticking

00:08:48.680 --> 00:08:50.870
and we are

00:08:50.880 --> 00:08:52.790
at

00:08:52.800 --> 00:08:54.670
the midnight

00:08:54.680 --> 00:08:57.590
hour. I'm telling you, it's time to wake

00:08:57.600 --> 00:08:59.750
up. And that's why I've tried to warn

00:08:59.760 --> 00:09:01.470
you over and over, even at the prayer

00:09:01.480 --> 00:09:04.110
conference, trying to warn the people

00:09:04.120 --> 00:09:07.550
that

00:09:07.560 --> 00:09:10.390
a major shaking is about to take place

00:09:10.400 --> 00:09:13.270
in this earth to awaken it. It's

00:09:13.280 --> 00:09:15.710
not just about America.

00:09:15.720 --> 00:09:17.270
President Trump said today,

00:09:17.280 --> 00:09:19.750
'Well, we have over 17 trillion dollars worth

00:09:19.760 --> 00:09:21.270
of stuff coming in.'I don't

00:09:21.280 --> 00:09:22.550
know where he's getting his numbers,

00:09:22.560 --> 00:09:25.110
but I pray that's

00:09:25.120 --> 00:09:29.950
true. I want an economic boom.

00:09:29.960 --> 00:09:34.470
I told you I saw the wave

00:09:34.480 --> 00:09:37.110
and it was transparent.

00:09:37.120 --> 00:09:39.830
You could see crypto,

00:09:39.840 --> 00:09:42.310
gold, silver,

00:09:42.310 --> 00:09:42.320
and

00:09:42.320 --> 00:09:44.870
the housing market through this.

00:09:44.880 --> 00:09:47.070
That means it was shallow.

00:09:47.080 --> 00:09:50.150
It wasn't a deep, defined wave,

00:09:50.160 --> 00:09:52.990
but it was a wave.

00:09:55.000 --> 00:09:56.510
Nevertheless, that's the word I

00:09:56.510 --> 00:09:56.520
would

00:09:56.520 --> 00:09:57.310
use.

00:09:57.320 --> 00:10:00.830
On top of the soil was gold.

00:10:00.840 --> 00:10:02.950
Do you all remember that?

00:10:02.960 --> 00:10:05.750
And the Lord said, 'There's enough gold

00:10:05.760 --> 00:10:07.870
on the layer of what's coming right

00:10:07.870 --> 00:10:07.880
here.'It

00:10:07.880 --> 00:10:10.110
was

00:10:10.110 --> 00:10:10.120
thin—not

00:10:10.120 --> 00:10:12.470
a thick foundation,

00:10:12.480 --> 00:10:14.430
