00:10:42.000 --> 00:10:44.030
the harvest.

00:10:44.040 --> 00:10:46.630
It's not going to be long-lived,

00:10:46.640 --> 00:10:48.230
but it will give you enough time and

00:10:48.240 --> 00:10:51.270
enough money to get the job done.

00:10:51.280 --> 00:10:53.630
Jesus Christ is coming,

00:10:53.640 --> 00:10:55.710
and I'm telling you, brush

00:10:55.710 --> 00:10:55.720
arbor

00:10:55.720 --> 00:10:59.350
Churches,

00:10:59.360 --> 00:11:01.390
Woodstock Church—it's like Woodstock,

00:11:01.400 --> 00:11:03.670
Holy Ghost Woodstock.

00:11:03.680 --> 00:11:05.910
All this is coming;

00:11:05.920 --> 00:11:07.910
it's right at our door.

