00:12:55.680 --> 00:12:58.110
a remnant of us who do, and

00:12:58.110 --> 00:12:58.120
those are

00:12:58.120 --> 00:12:59.630
the ones I believe

00:12:59.640 --> 00:13:01.230
are coming on here praying every single

00:13:01.240 --> 00:13:02.310
time we

00:13:02.320 --> 00:13:04.150
start prayer, and you're

00:13:04.160 --> 00:13:06.710
excited about it.

00:13:06.720 --> 00:13:10.510
Hey, this is a cool book: In Him by

00:13:10.520 --> 00:13:12.270
Kenneth E. Hagin.

00:13:12.280 --> 00:13:16.310
It's a little short read;

00:13:16.320 --> 00:13:18.590
it's 32 pages. I bet it's less than a

