00:14:01.760 --> 00:14:03.190
The Precious

00:14:03.200 --> 00:14:06.590
Blood of Jesus by Kenneth E. Hagin.

00:14:06.600 --> 00:14:09.910
And then she got me The Gifts of

00:14:09.920 --> 00:14:12.590
Prophecy by Kenneth E. Hagin.

00:14:12.600 --> 00:14:16.110
And then she got me Praying to Get

00:14:16.120 --> 00:14:19.750
Results

00:14:19.760 --> 00:14:21.350
